</paramdef>

</funcprototype>
</funcsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>
<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
The interface <function>srand48_r</function> shall function in the same
way as the interface <function>srand48</function>, except that
<function>srand48_r</function> shall
use the data in
<parameter>buffer</parameter> instead of the global random 
number generator state.
</para>
</refsect1>
